{"name":"zflickjs","body":"### もくてき\r\niOS, Androidのみで提供するサービスではjQueryなどのライブラリを使わず、ネイティブで実装した方がパフォーマンス良いんじゃないかと思ってみた。\r\n\r\n### セットアップ\r\n<head>タグ内にzflick.cssとzflick.jsを読み込む。\r\n```\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"zflick.css\">\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"zflick.js\"></script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n下記のようにHTMLを組む。高速化のためにJSで動かす要素はID指定になっている。\r\n```\r\n<div id=\"zflickjs\">\r\n  <div id=\"zcontents\" class=\"group contents\">\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"126x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"126x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"126x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"126x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n    <div class=\"zcol\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"zlink\"><img src=\"48x48.gif\"></a></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"group\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em;\">\r\n  <span id=\"prev\" class=\"zflickClickBtn\" style=\"float: left;\">prev</span>\r\n  <span id=\"next\" class=\"zflickClickBtn\" style=\"float: right;\">next</span>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\nnew zflickjs({})で初期化\r\n```\r\n<script>\r\nvar init = function(){\r\n  new zflickjs({\r\n    id: 'zflickjs',\r\n    contents: 'zcontents',\r\n    col: 'zcol',\r\n    margin: 10,\r\n    btn: {\r\n      prev: 'prev',\r\n      next: 'next'\r\n    }\r\n  });\r\n}\r\nwindow.addEventListener('load', init, false);\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Support or Contact\r\ntwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/funnythingz\" target=\"_blank\">@funnythingz</a>","tagline":"iOS, Android に特化した超軽量なflickjsを頑張ってつくるよ！CSS3 + JavaScript で。","google":"UA-1882060-12","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}